        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Energy Savings and Industrial Competitiveness Act</b> <b>of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill revises a variety of programs to encourage energy efficiency in buildings, industry, and the federal government, including by encouraging</p> <ul> <li>energy efficiency in residential, commercial, federal, or school buildings;</li> <li>energy-efficient technologies and processes for industrial applications;</li> <li>sustainable manufacturing;</li> <li>energy-efficient electric motors or transformers; or</li> <li>federal use of energy-efficient and energy-saving information technologies.</li> </ul>]]></text>
      </summary>
